entries.femaleVariant: He's lettin' 'er go?!
Better have a quick fuckin' change of heart.
What, can't lay a finger on her all of a sudden?
entries.maleVariant: What, can't lay a finger on him all of a sudden?

entries.femaleVariant: Like I give a shit.
The fuck're you all standing around holding your dicks for, huh?
The hell we s'posed to do?
Got ears, choomba? He said he doesn't want any problems.
Grrrr... But I'ma remember that puny-ass muzzle.
Gather your kit. Get movin'.
What? Who? Did anyone see her?
entries.maleVariant: What? Wh-who? Did anyone see him?

entries.femaleVariant: Wait, so she's NetWatch too?
She look like NetWatch to you, fleabrain?
entries.maleVariant: He look like NetWatch to you, fleabrain?

entries.femaleVariant: Seriously? Let her go? Just like that?
entries.maleVariant: Seriously? Let 'im go? Just like that?

entries.femaleVariant: That's what the man said.
The fuck're you all standin' around gawkin' for?
What the fuck's goin' on here?
Didn't help you spot her before, and it's sure as shit a waste of time now.
entries.maleVariant: Didn't help you spot him before, and it's sure as shit a waste of time now.

entries.femaleVariant: The hell are we s'posed to do, then?
Grab your gear. Move!
I'm gonna gut that bitch!
Ice it, choomba. He said to let her go.
entries.maleVariant: Ice it, choomba. He said to let him go.

entries.femaleVariant: And no one saw her?
What the fuck's goin' on here?
Let her go, man.
Gonna remember your face, bitch!
entries.maleVariant: Gonna remember your face, you motherfucker!

entries.femaleVariant: I don't give a fuck who's protectin' her or why!
entries.maleVariant: I don't give a fuck who's protectin' him or why!

entries.femaleVariant: Levi, Gecko, Argus – all dead 'cause of her!
entries.maleVariant: Levi, Gecko, Argus – all dead 'cause of him!

entries.femaleVariant: Know how many of us she flatlined?!
entries.maleVariant: Know how many of us he flatlined?!

entries.femaleVariant: I know, man. But 'member – she's fair game once she leaves...
entries.maleVariant: I know, man. But 'member – he's fair game once he leaves...

entries.femaleVariant: What the shit... She the one who flatlined our guys?
entries.maleVariant: What the shit... He the one who flatlined our guys?

entries.femaleVariant: Argh! C'mon, I'll fuckin'--!
Fuck no, over my dead body.
But that chairjock from NetWatch said--
There a problem?
Just one. And I can solve it right now.
No. Now move the fuck out. End of topic.
I wanna know the dead man who sent her.
entries.maleVariant: I wanna know the dead man who sent him.

entries.femaleVariant: Does it matter? You can't bring 'em back.
The fuck is this? Coffee break?
Who's that bitch? You even know?
No, and I don't give a cat's ass.
She ain't leavin' in one piece.
entries.maleVariant: He ain't leavin' in one piece.

entries.femaleVariant: Oh, and all the guys from our pack who died – couldn't give a shit, either?
They had a job. Be strong. She was stronger. End of story.
entries.maleVariant: They had a job. Be strong. He was stronger. End of story.

entries.femaleVariant: I don't take orders from no one 'cept 'Squatch!
